/authorities/html/90536426">Base de bibliothèque norvégienne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://aut.nkp.cz/kv2013742559">Bibliothèque nationale tchèque</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n86-075796">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
