ano</a> (2014)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Svetlana_Aleksievitch" title="Svetlana Aleksievitch">Aleksievitch</a> (2015)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Bob_Dylan" title="Bob Dylan">Dylan</a> (2016)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Kazuo_Ishiguro" title="Kazuo Ishiguro">Ishiguro</a> (2017)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Olga_Tokarczuk" title="Olga Tokarczuk">Tokarczuk</a> (2018)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Peter_Handke" title="Peter Handke">Handke</a> (2019)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Louise_Gl%C3%BCck" title="Louise Glück">Glück</a> (2020)</span></td>
